{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Fix and rebuild the Dynamic FAQ section.
    
    The current FAQ section is not functional. It is showing the FAQ title/question, but the answer/details are not opening or not displaying correctly.
    
    The section must load FAQs from the page metafield:
    
    custom.faqs
    
    This metafield is a List of FAQ metaobject references.
    
    Use this Liquid source:
    
    page.metafields.custom.faqs.value
    
    Each FAQ metaobject has these field keys:
    
    question
    answer
    category
    display_order
    target_service
    target_suburb
    target_item
    seo_keywords
    
    Important:
    The Answer field is a Rich Text field, so it must be rendered correctly using Shopify Liquid rich text output.
    
    Do not hardcode FAQ content.
    Do not use manual blocks.
    Loop through the selected FAQ metaobjects.
    
    If custom.faqs is empty, hide the full FAQ section.
    
    FAQ layout:
    
    - Display section heading: Frequently Asked Questions
    - Display subheading: Helpful answers about our furniture delivery, marketplace pickup, pricing and same-day delivery services.
    - Display Category as a small badge if it exists.
    - Display Question as the accordion button.
    - Display Answer inside the accordion panel.
    - Hide empty fields.
    - Sort FAQs by display_order if possible.
    
    Accordion behaviour:
    
    - First FAQ should be open by default.
    - Clicking a question opens its answer.
    - Clicking it again closes it.
    - Only one FAQ should be open at a time.
    - Each FAQ must have a unique ID.
    - Use button elements for questions.
    - Add aria-expanded and aria-controls.
    - Make it keyboard accessible.
    
    Design:
    
    - Premium modern FAQ design.
    - White rounded cards.
    - Soft shadow.
    - Clean spacing.
    - Mobile friendly.
    - Plus/minus SVG icon.
    - Smooth open/close animation.
    - Maximum width around 900px.
    - Centered section.
    
    SEO:
    
    - Use semantic HTML.
    - Use <section>.
    - Heading should be <h2>.
    - Each FAQ should be inside <article>.
    - Generate FAQPage JSON-LD from the selected FAQ metaobjects.
    - Use the same Question and Answer values in the schema.
    - Strip HTML from Answer in schema.
    - Do not generate schema if there are no FAQs.
    - Do not generate duplicate schema.
    
    Performance:
    
    - Use Shopify Liquid.
    - Use CSS.
    - Use vanilla JavaScript only.
    - No jQuery.
    - No external libraries.
    
    Important debugging requirements:
    
    - Make sure the answer panel is not hidden permanently by CSS.
    - Make sure JavaScript targets the correct FAQ buttons and panels.
    - Make sure rich text answers display properly.
    - Make sure the section works on both desktop and mobile.
    - Make sure no answer content appears blank if the metaobject answer field has content.
    
    Final goal:
    
    A fully working dynamic FAQ accordion that automatically displays all FAQ metaobjects assigned to each page through custom.faqs., Fix the Dynamic FAQ section.
    
    The FAQ answer is currently showing raw rich text JSON like:
    {"type":"root","children"...}
    
    This is wrong.
    
    The FAQ answer field is a Shopify Rich Text metafield/metaobject field.
    
    Render the answer properly as formatted HTML/text, not as raw JSON.
    
    Use Shopify Liquid rich text rendering.
    
    For each FAQ:
    
    {% assign answer_content = faq.answer | metafield_tag %}
    
    Display:
    {{ answer_content }}
    
    Do not display:
    {{ faq.answer }}
    or
    {{ faq.answer.value }}
    
    because that outputs raw JSON.
    
    Also update the FAQPage JSON-LD schema so the answer is converted to plain text by stripping HTML.
    
    Requirements:
    
    - Load FAQs from page.metafields.custom.faqs.value
    - Loop through selected FAQ metaobjects
    - Display category
    - Display question
    - Display rich text answer correctly
    - Accordion must open and close
    - First FAQ open by default
    - Hide section if no FAQs exist
    - Use Liquid, CSS, and vanilla JavaScript only, Make it Mobile Friendly , Create a Shopify section called Dynamic FAQ.
    
    Load FAQs from page.metafields.custom.faqs.value.
    
    This is a list of FAQ metaobject references.
    
    Each FAQ has these fields:
    question
    answer
    category
    display_order
    icon
    helpful_tip
    cta_text
    cta_link
    related_services
    related_suburbs
    featured_faq
    
    Loop through all selected FAQs.
    
    Display:
    - Category badge
    - Icon
    - Question
    - Answer using metafield_tag because answer is rich text
    - Helpful Tip using metafield_tag if available
    - CTA button if CTA Text and CTA Link exist
    - Related Services as chips
    - Related Suburbs as chips
    - Featured badge if Featured FAQ is true
    
    Make it a premium accordion:
    - First FAQ open by default
    - Only one open at a time
    - Plus/minus icon
    - Smooth animation
    - Mobile friendly
    - White cards
    - Rounded corners
    - Soft shadow
    - Good spacing
    
    Important:
    For rich text fields, use metafield_tag.
    Do not output raw JSON.
    
    Hide empty fields.
    Hide entire section if no FAQs are assigned.
    
    Generate FAQPage JSON-LD from question and answer.
    Use plain text for schema answers.
    Use Liquid, CSS and vanilla JavaScript only.
    No external libraries.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}
{% assign faqs = page.metafields.custom.faqs.value %}

{% if faqs.size > 0 %}
  {% assign sorted_faqs = faqs | sort: 'display_order' %}

  {% style %}
    .ai-faq-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top }}px 20px {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom }}px 20px;
      background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    }

    .ai-faq-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      max-width: {{ block.settings.max_width }}px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .ai-faq-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    .ai-faq-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size }}px;
      color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .ai-faq-subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.subheading_size }}px;
      color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
      margin: 0;
      opacity: 0.8;
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .ai-faq-list-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: {{ block.settings.item_spacing }}px;
    }

    .ai-faq-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      background-color: {{ block.settings.card_background }};
      border-radius: {{ block.settings.border_radius }}px;
      box-shadow: 0 {{ block.settings.shadow_vertical }}px {{ block.settings.shadow_blur }}px rgba(0, 0, 0, {{ block.settings.shadow_opacity }});
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
      position: relative;
    }

    .ai-faq-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 {{ block.settings.shadow_vertical | plus: 2 }}px {{ block.settings.shadow_blur | plus: 4 }}px rgba(0, 0, 0, {{ block.settings.shadow_opacity | times: 1.5 | at_most: 1 }});
    }

    .ai-faq-featured-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      position: absolute;
      top: 16px;
      right: 16px;
      background-color: {{ block.settings.featured_badge_bg }};
      color: {{ block.settings.featured_badge_color }};
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .ai-faq-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      padding: {{ block.settings.padding_vertical }}px {{ block.settings.padding_horizontal }}px;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      text-align: left;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .ai-faq-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
    }

    .ai-faq-button-left-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .ai-faq-icon-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background-color: {{ block.settings.icon_bg_color }};
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .ai-faq-icon-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
      width: 18px;
      height: 18px;
      fill: {{ block.settings.icon_color }};
    }

    .ai-faq-button-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .ai-faq-category-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      background-color: {{ block.settings.category_background }};
      color: {{ block.settings.category_text_color }};
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .ai-faq-question-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.question_size }}px;
      color: {{ block.settings.question_color }};
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.4;
      word-wrap: break-word;
      overflow-wrap: break-word;
    }

    .ai-faq-toggle-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      margin-top: 2px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .ai-faq-toggle-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      stroke: {{ block.settings.toggle_icon_color }};
      stroke-width: 2;
    }

    .ai-faq-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}[aria-expanded="true"] .ai-faq-toggle-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      transform: rotate(45deg);
    }

    .ai-faq-panel-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      max-height: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: max-height 0.4s ease, padding 0.4s ease;
    }

    .ai-faq-panel-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
      max-height: 5000px;
      padding: 0 {{ block.settings.padding_horizontal }}px {{ block.settings.padding_vertical }}px {{ block.settings.padding_horizontal }}px;
    }

    .ai-faq-panel-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding-left: 44px;
    }

    .ai-faq-answer-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.answer_size }}px;
      color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
      line-height: 1.7;
      word-wrap: break-word;
      overflow-wrap: break-word;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .ai-faq-answer-{{ ai_gen_id }} p {
      margin: 0 0 12px 0;
    }

    .ai-faq-answer-{{ ai_gen_id }} p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .ai-faq-answer-{{ ai_gen_id }} ul,
    .ai-faq-answer-{{ ai_gen_id }} ol {
      margin: 12px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .ai-faq-answer-{{ ai_gen_id }} li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .ai-faq-answer-{{ ai_gen_id }} strong {
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .ai-faq-answer-{{ ai_gen_id }} a {
      color: {{ block.settings.link_color }};
      text-decoration: underline;
      word-break: break-word;
    }

    .ai-faq-tip-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      background-color: {{ block.settings.tip_bg_color }};
      border-left: 3px solid {{ block.settings.tip_border_color }};
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-size: {{ block.settings.answer_size }}px;
      color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .ai-faq-tip-{{ ai_gen_id }} p {
      margin: 0;
    }

    .ai-faq-cta-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: {{ block.settings.cta_bg_color }};
      color: {{ block.settings.cta_text_color }};
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: {{ block.settings.cta_border_radius }}px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .ai-faq-cta-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
      background-color: {{ block.settings.cta_hover_bg_color }};
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .ai-faq-chips-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .ai-faq-chip-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 6px 14px;
      background-color: {{ block.settings.chip_bg_color }};
      color: {{ block.settings.chip_text_color }};
      font-size: 13px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid {{ block.settings.chip_border_color }};
    }

    .ai-faq-chips-label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
      opacity: 0.7;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
      .ai-faq-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top | times: 0.7 | round }}px 16px {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom | times: 0.7 | round }}px 16px;
      }

      .ai-faq-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        margin-bottom: 32px;
      }

      .ai-faq-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size | times: 0.65 | round }}px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }

      .ai-faq-subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        font-size: {{ block.settings.subheading_size | times: 0.9 | round }}px;
      }

      .ai-faq-list-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        gap: {{ block.settings.item_spacing | times: 0.75 | round }}px;
      }

      .ai-faq-question-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        font-size: {{ block.settings.question_size | times: 0.9 | round }}px;
      }

      .ai-faq-answer-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        font-size: {{ block.settings.answer_size | times: 0.95 | round }}px;
      }

      .ai-faq-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        padding: {{ block.settings.padding_vertical | times: 0.75 | round }}px {{ block.settings.padding_horizontal | times: 0.7 | round }}px;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .ai-faq-panel-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
        padding: 0 {{ block.settings.padding_horizontal | times: 0.7 | round }}px {{ block.settings.padding_vertical | times: 0.75 | round }}px {{ block.settings.padding_horizontal | times: 0.7 | round }}px;
      }

      .ai-faq-panel-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        padding-left: 0;
      }

      .ai-faq-button-left-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        gap: 10px;
      }

      .ai-faq-icon-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        width: 28px;
        height: 28px;
      }

      .ai-faq-icon-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
        width: 16px;
        height: 16px;
      }

      .ai-faq-toggle-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
      }

      .ai-faq-category-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        font-size: 10px;
        padding: 3px 10px;
      }

      .ai-faq-featured-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        font-size: 10px;
        padding: 3px 10px;
        top: 12px;
        right: 12px;
      }

      .ai-faq-answer-{{ ai_gen_id }} ul,
      .ai-faq-answer-{{ ai_gen_id }} ol {
        padding-left: 16px;
      }

      .ai-faq-tip-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        padding: 12px;
        font-size: {{ block.settings.answer_size | times: 0.95 | round }}px;
      }

      .ai-faq-cta-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        padding: 10px 20px;
        font-size: 13px;
      }

      .ai-faq-chip-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        font-size: 12px;
        padding: 5px 12px;
      }
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
      .ai-faq-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top | times: 0.6 | round }}px 12px {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom | times: 0.6 | round }}px 12px;
      }

      .ai-faq-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size | times: 0.55 | round }}px;
      }

      .ai-faq-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        padding: {{ block.settings.padding_vertical | times: 0.65 | round }}px {{ block.settings.padding_horizontal | times: 0.6 | round }}px;
      }

      .ai-faq-panel-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
        padding: 0 {{ block.settings.padding_horizontal | times: 0.6 | round }}px {{ block.settings.padding_vertical | times: 0.65 | round }}px {{ block.settings.padding_horizontal | times: 0.6 | round }}px;
      }
    }
  {% endstyle %}

  <faq-accordion-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-faq-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
    <section class="ai-faq-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.section_heading != blank or block.settings.section_subheading != blank %}
        <div class="ai-faq-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if block.settings.section_heading != blank %}
            <h2 class="ai-faq-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.section_heading }}</h2>
          {% endif %}
          {% if block.settings.section_subheading != blank %}
            <p class="ai-faq-subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.section_subheading }}</p>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      {% endif %}

      <div class="ai-faq-list-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% for faq in sorted_faqs %}
          {% assign faq_index = forloop.index %}
          {% assign faq_id = ai_gen_id | append: '-faq-' | append: faq_index %}
          {% assign answer_content = faq.answer | metafield_tag %}
          {% assign helpful_tip_content = faq.helpful_tip | metafield_tag %}
          
          <article class="ai-faq-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% if faq.featured_faq == true %}
              <span class="ai-faq-featured-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.featured_label }}</span>
            {% endif %}

            <button
              class="ai-faq-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              aria-expanded="{% if forloop.first %}true{% else %}false{% endif %}"
              aria-controls="{{ faq_id }}"
              data-faq-button
            >
              <div class="ai-faq-button-left-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {% if faq.icon != blank %}
                  <div class="ai-faq-icon-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    {{ faq.icon }}
                  </div>
                {% endif %}
                <div class="ai-faq-button-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {% if faq.category != blank %}
                    <span class="ai-faq-category-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ faq.category }}</span>
                  {% endif %}
                  <h3 class="ai-faq-question-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ faq.question }}</h3>
                </div>
              </div>
              <span class="ai-faq-toggle-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"></line>
                  <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line>
                </svg>
              </span>
            </button>

            <div
              id="{{ faq_id }}"
              class="ai-faq-panel-{{ ai_gen_id }}{% if forloop.first %} active{% endif %}"
              data-faq-panel
            >
              <div class="ai-faq-panel-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {% if answer_content != blank %}
                  <div class="ai-faq-answer-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    {{ answer_content }}
                  </div>
                {% endif %}

                {% if helpful_tip_content != blank %}
                  <div class="ai-faq-tip-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    {{ helpful_tip_content }}
                  </div>
                {% endif %}

                {% if faq.cta_text != blank and faq.cta_link != blank %}
                  <a href="{{ faq.cta_link }}" class="ai-faq-cta-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    {{ faq.cta_text }}
                  </a>
                {% endif %}

                {% if faq.related_services != blank %}
                  <div>
                    <div class="ai-faq-chips-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">Related Services</div>
                    <div class="ai-faq-chips-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                      {% assign services = faq.related_services | split: ',' %}
                      {% for service in services %}
                        <span class="ai-faq-chip-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ service | strip }}</span>
                      {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                  </div>
                {% endif %}

                {% if faq.related_suburbs != blank %}
                  <div>
                    <div class="ai-faq-chips-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">Related Suburbs</div>
                    <div class="ai-faq-chips-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                      {% assign suburbs = faq.related_suburbs | split: ',' %}
                      {% for suburb in suburbs %}
                        <span class="ai-faq-chip-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ suburb | strip }}</span>
                      {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                  </div>
                {% endif %}
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </section>
  </faq-accordion-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

  {% if block.settings.enable_schema %}
    <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "FAQPage",
      "mainEntity": [
        {% for faq in sorted_faqs %}
          {% assign answer_html = faq.answer | metafield_tag %}
          {% assign answer_text = answer_html | strip_html %}
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": {{ faq.question | json }},
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": {{ answer_text | json }}
            }
          }{% unless forloop.last %},{% endunless %}
        {% endfor %}
      ]
    }
    </script>
  {% endif %}

  <script>
    (function() {
      class FaqAccordion{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
        constructor() {
          super();
        }

        connectedCallback() {
          this.buttons = this.querySelectorAll('[data-faq-button]');
          this.panels = this.querySelectorAll('[data-faq-panel]');
          this.setupEventListeners();
        }

        setupEventListeners() {
          this.buttons.forEach((button, index) => {
            button.addEventListener('click', () => {
              this.toggleFaq(index);
            });

            button.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
              if (e.key === 'Enter' || e.key === ' ') {
                e.preventDefault();
                this.toggleFaq(index);
              }
            });
          });
        }

        toggleFaq(index) {
          const button = this.buttons[index];
          const panel = this.panels[index];
          const isExpanded = button.getAttribute('aria-expanded') === 'true';

          this.buttons.forEach((btn, i) => {
            if (i !== index) {
              btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');
              this.panels[i].classList.remove('active');
            }
          });

          button.setAttribute('aria-expanded', !isExpanded);
          panel.classList.toggle('active');
        }
      }

      customElements.define('faq-accordion-{{ ai_gen_id }}', FaqAccordion{{ ai_gen_id }});
    })();
  </script>
{% endif %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Dynamic FAQ",
  "tag": null,
  "settings": [
    {
